description:
This is a 39 minute workout called '30 MIN GUIDED PILATES WORKOUT TO BUILD MUSCLE & LOSE FAT- At Home Pilates Strength' from the channel Olivia Lawson.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Join me for a full body Pilates inspired strength class that focuses on building muscle, burning fat, strengthening your core and upper body. This is a guided, no repeats, interval style class with 15s rest periods, that will allow you to change your equipment (if needed) and prepare for the next exercise. 

Equipment needed:
- 2 sets of  dumbbells ( in my case- 2kg/ 4.4lb, 3kg/ 6.6lb)
- non slip mat
